{% set showHeader = showComponentTitle != false %}
<section class="disclosure-group{% if not showHeader %} disclosure-group-plain{% endif %}" aria-label="Services">

{% if showHeader %}
<details>

<summary class="disclosure-header">
MY SERVICES
</summary>
{% endif %}

<div class="content-block">

<details class="disclosure-item">
<summary>Individual Psychotherapy (NY & ME)</summary>
<div class="content-block">
<hr class="rule dotted-blue-rule">

<p>I offer talk therapy to individuals who have acute psychiatric symptoms that justify clinical care. Clients are often responding to a significant incident in life, such as education disruption, high conflict divorce, legal issues, or a relational problems driven by unwanted behaviors and moods.</p>

<hr class="rule dotted-blue-rule">

<p>Want to start the conversation? I offer free consultations</p>
<a href="#contact-me" class="button" id="schedule-consultation">
  Message Me
</a>

</div>
</details>



<details class="disclosure-item">
<summary>Social Work-Informed Consulting</summary>
<hr class="rule dotted-blue-rule">
<div class="content-block">
<p>
For individuals with less psychiatrically acute problems and contexts, I offer consulting services. Consultees are often students, tradesmen, servicemen, developers, or creative professionals. Most desire a fresh perspective and new pathways in their self-development.

Consulting differs from psychotherapy in a few key ways:

* They follow different ethical standards.
* Consulting is non-clinical, with simpler documentation and no insurance billing.
* The focus is on professional and interpersonal goals first; behavior change and symptom reduction are secondary.
* My consulting is subscription-based and tailored to your needs.


</p>

<hr class="rule dotted-blue-rule">

<p>Want to see if this service is right for you? Drop me a line.</p>
<a href="#contact-me" class="button" id="schedule-consultation">
  Message Me
</a>

</div>



</details>
</div>

{% if showHeader %}
</details>
{% endif %}

</section>